      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">{pageTitle}</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          Navigate property markets with confidence using our analytical frameworks. We cover:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Market cycle analysis</li>
          <li>Investment property evaluation</li>
          <li>Financing strategies</li>
          <li>Tax optimization</li>
          <li>Emerging market opportunities</li>
